Subject: drm/xe/vf: Return EOPNOTSUPP for DRM_XE_DEVICE_QUERY_ENGINE_CYCLES if
 VF
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 5a9f8db2db70e09b47010a936b6c4fb83975464f
